-nile-cruise\">{{cite web |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-egypt/egypt-confirms-33-new-cases-of-coronavirus-on-nile-cruise-ship-idUSKBN20U0TK |title=Egypt confirms 33 new cases of coronavirus on Nile cruise ship |work=[[Reuters]] |date=7 March 2020 |access-date=17 March 2020 |first1=Mai Shams |last1=Eddin |first2=Samar |last2=Hassan |first3=Aidan |last3=Lewis |first4=Kevin |last4=Liffey |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200316080749/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-egypt/egypt-confirms-33-new-cases-of-coronavirus-on-nile-cruise-ship-idUSKBN20U0TK |archive-date=16 March 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n| 70<ref name=\"ship-nile-cruise\" />\n| 171<ref name=\"ship-nile-cruise\" />\n| 7 March<ref name=\"ship-nile-cruise\" />\n| [[Luxor]]<ref name=\"ship-nile-cruise\" />\n| [[Egypt]]\n| Extension Group<ref name=\"cruise-owner-ms-a-sara.1\">http://www.extensiongroup.com.eg/about.html</ref><ref name=\"cruise-owner-ms-a-sara.2\">http://www.extensiongroup.com.eg/asara.html</ref>\n| \n| 45<ref name=Twitter1236347954593759232/>\n| \n|-\n\n| {{ship||Voyager of the Seas}}<ref name=\"ship-voyager-of-the-seas-first\">{{cite web |url=https://www.health.nsw.gov.au/news/Pages/20200322_00.aspx |title=COVID-19 (Coronavirus) statistics |work=NSW Government |date= |access-date=23 March 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200322033800/https://www.health.nsw.gov.au/news/Pages/20200322_00.aspx |archive-date=22 March 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref> \n| \n| \n| \n| 7 March<ref name=\"ship-voyager-of-the-seas-first\" />\n| [[Port Jackson|Sydney Harbour]]{{efn|[[Sydney]]|name=\"sydney\"}}<ref name=\"ship-voyager-of-the-seas-first\" />\n| [[Australia]]\n| Royal Caribbean<ref name=\"cruise-owner-voyager-of-the-seas\">{{cite web |url=https://www.royalcaribbean.com/cruise-ships/voyager-of-the-seas |title=Voyager of the Seas |work=Royal Caribbean |date= |access-date=23 March 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200323161927