ow\" />\n| [[Brazil]]\n| [[Silversea Cruises]]{{efn|Part of [[Royal Caribbean Cruises|Royal Caribbean]]|name=\"royal\"}}<ref name=\"cruise-owner-silversea-royalcaribbean\">{{cite web |url=https://www.silversea.com/other-resources/press-releases/2018/july-/royal-caribbean-completes-acquisition-of-silversea-cruises-share.html |title=Royal Caribbean Completes Acquisition of Silversea Cruises Shares |work=Silversea.com |date= |access-date=17 March 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200331180729/https://www.silversea.com/other-resources/press-releases/2018/july-/royal-caribbean-completes-acquisition-of-silversea-cruises-share.html |archive-date=31 March 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref><ref name=\"cruise-owner2-silversea-royalcaribbean\">{{cite web |url=https://www.silversea.com/ships/silver-shadow.html |title=Silver Shadow |work=Silversea.com |date= |access-date=17 March 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200331180730/https://www.silversea.com/ships/silver-shadow.html |archive-date=31 March 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n| \n| \n| \n|-\n\n| {{ship||Silver Explorer}}\n| 111<ref name=\"ship-silver-explorer\">{{cite news |url=https://www.cnn.com/travel/article/cruise-ships-stranded-coronavirus-trnd/index.html |title=Multiple cruise ships are left stranded as coronavirus cases increase |work=CNN.com |date= |access-date=16 March 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200316001502/https://www.cnn.com/travel/article/cruise-ships-stranded-coronavirus-trnd/index.html |archive-date=16 March 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n| 120<ref name=\"ship-silver-explorer\" />\n| 231    \n| 14 March<ref name=\"ship-silver-explorer\" />\n| [[Castro, Chile|Castro]]{{efn|[[Chilo\u00e9 Island]], [[Los Lagos Region|Los Lagos]]}}<ref name=\"ship-silver-explorer\" />         \n| [[Chile]]\n| [[Silversea Cruises]]{{efn|name=\"royal\"}}<ref name=\"cruise-owner-silversea-royalcaribbean\" /><ref name=\"cruise-owner2-silverexplorer-royalcaribbean\">{{cite web |url=https:/